data.description: Wonderful home in Sandy Creek. Move-in ready! This 3 bedroom,2 bath is perfect! Split bedroom floor plan, Beautiful detail thru out, with plenty of natural lighting. Kitchen features granite countertops, gas stove, stained cabinets and refrigerator conveys. Main bedroom is very spacious with tiled walk in shower and a large closet! Backyard is ready for all types of entertainment! Great curb appeal! Come and take a look at your new home!
